    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD-predicted NIH values agreed with experimental measurements within 12% across all five operating points, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
